    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div><div class="line">25</div><div class="line">26</div><div class="line">27</div><div class="line">28</div><div class="line">29</div><div class="line">30</div><div class="line">31</div><div class="line">32</div><div class="line">33</div><div class="line">34</div><div class="line">35</div><div class="line">36</div><div class="line">37</div><div class="line">38</div><div class="line">39</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">1.京东移动端的搜索框,把header的左边pandding值设置的长度应该和左边所在的logo的宽度相等.</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">2.less调用函数的时候需要加.</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">3. background-origin: content-box;</div><div class="line">    background-clip: content-box;   ?</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">4.关于less等层级关系 如果写的不对样式添加不进去  可以优先检查</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">5.一共有8个span  选中3 6  nth:child(3n)</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">6.border-radius 做椭圆形  用50%</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">7.nth-child()  意义在于第几个子元素(不管第一个子元素与第二个子元素是否相同)</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">8.</div><div class="line">我是一个表	nth-child（）	   莫用</div><div class="line">奇数偶数	  nth-child（2n）	 偶数项选中</div><div class="line">技术偶数	  nth-child（2n-1）   奇数项选中</div><div class="line">区间         nth-child(n+4）	 选中大于4的项</div><div class="line">区间	     nth-child（-n+4）   选中小于4的项</div><div class="line">间隔区间	 nth-child(3n+1)	 隔二选一</div><div class="line">间隔区间	 nth-child(3n)	   隔三选一</div><div class="line">从后数数	 nth-last-child()	倒着数哦</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">9.vertical-align? 行内居中</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">10.因为精度问题 浮动不上去(或者偶尔上偶尔下),把浮动不上去的元素 clear:both ?</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">11.滚动条事件 windows.onscroll = func</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">12.获取页面被卷去的高度</div><div class="line">	scrollTop = document.doucmentElement.scrollTop || document.body.scrollTop;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">13.不能直接用opacity直接设置顶部栏透明度	 必须要颜色透明度rgb拼接字符串</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">14.添加监听事件 transitionend 运动完毕</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">15.返回的必须是return函数 才可以赋值</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
